Package uni.bielefeld.cmg.sparkhit.struct

This package contains different classes as data structures used for sequence alignment.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlignmentParameter
    A data structure class that stores all parameters for sequence alignment.
    BinaryBlock
    A data structure class that stores a k-mer block in binary.
    Block
    A data structure class that stores the locus of each binary block.
    CandidateBlock
    A data structure class that stores the locus of each candidate block.
    HitInfo
    A data structure class that stores the locus of each k-mer match.
    KmerLoc
    A data structure class that stores the loci of all k-mers on the reference genome.
    Qgram
    A data structure class that stores all parameters for a Q-gram.
    QgramComparator
    A comparator class for comparing the q-gram scores of all the q-grams.
    ReadInfo
    A data structure class that stores all parameters for a sequence read.
    RefInfo
    A data structure class that stores all parameters for a reference genome.
    RefTitle
    A data structure class that stores all names of reference contigs (scaffolds or chromosomes).
